      <title>中国准备从印度购买更多产品，因为美国关税织机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/china-ready-to-buy-more-products-from-india-as-us-tariffs-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北京大使Xu Feihong说，中国愿意购买更多印度产品来平衡贸易，并在美国关税公告预计将袭击南亚邻国之前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/china-ready-to-buy-more-products-from-india-as-us-tariffs-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 09:13:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税动荡激发了贸易律师的疯狂工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-s-tariff-upheaval-sparks-frenzy-of-work-for-trade-lawyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[制造商和供应商受到简单供求的约束。还有合同，规则，法律，仲裁条款和其他众多法律规定，使商业流动顺利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-s-tariff-upheaval-sparks-frenzy-of-work-for-trade-lawyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）向选民付款，将现金投入8200万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/elon-musk-s-wisconsin-supreme-court-fight-is-all-about-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）正在寻求重复他与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统取得的政治胜利，该胜利通过将数百万美元部署到美国历史上最昂贵的司法竞赛中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/elon-musk-s-wisconsin-supreme-court-fight-is-all-about-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在特朗普申请批评之后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/ukraine-pushing-ahead-on-us-deal-after-trump-renews-criticism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰的顶级外交官说，在唐纳德·特朗普总统指责基夫试图重新谈判这笔交易的几个小时后，官员们向美国敦促向美国迈向“可接受的”经济协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/ukraine-pushing-ahead-on-us-deal-after-trump-renews-criticism</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 08:50:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安（Erdogan）入狱的竞争对手呼吁抵制与国家联系品牌的抵制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/erdogan-s-jailed-rival-calls-for-boycott-of-state-linked-brands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其被判入狱的反对派人物埃克雷姆·伊玛莫格鲁（Ekrem Imamoglu）敦促支持者抵制被视为与政府圈子有关的实体，因为上个月被捕后继续进行抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/erdogan-s-jailed-rival-calls-for-boycott-of-state-linked-brands</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 08:41:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉扩大了欧洲低迷，法国的销售额下降了37％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/tesla-extends-european-slump-with-37-sales-drop-in-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司上个月在法国的销售额下降了37％，因为电动车制造商继续在欧洲的表现不佳，埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）参与政治和模型的转换是主要的障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/tesla-extends-european-slump-with-37-sales-drop-in-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 08:22:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在4月2日的关税之前猛击印度高印度对农用商品的职责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-slams-high-india-duties-on-farm-goods-before-april-2-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）政府强调了印度对美国农业商品的高关税，就在互惠关税开始之前的几天，向南亚国家施加了进一步的压力，要求减少对政治敏感农业部门的遏制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-slams-high-india-duties-on-farm-goods-before-april-2-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 08:11:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士冷冻俄罗斯资产塔利跃升至84亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/swiss-froze-28-more-russian-assets-in-past-year-following-eu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士当局冻结的俄罗斯资产价值跃升至74亿瑞士法郎（84亿美元），因为该国对数百名被视为接近克里姆林宫的俄罗斯个人和公司采取了进一步的欧洲联盟的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/swiss-froze-28-more-russian-assets-in-past-year-following-eu</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 07:41:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>兰德（Rand）滑倒是南非预算的僵持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/rand-gyrates-as-south-african-politicians-debate-crucial-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的兰特（Rand）削弱了联盟政府的两个最大政党的政客继续进行的谈判，目的是解决国家预算的争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/rand-gyrates-as-south-african-politicians-debate-crucial-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 05:52:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Le Pen选举禁令风险在法国政治中脆弱的平静</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/le-pen-election-ban-threatens-fragile-peace-in-french-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[海洋勒庞（Marine Le Pen）的选举禁令有法国反建立情绪的激增，这可能会破坏稳定美国吱吱作响的公共财政的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/le-pen-election-ban-threatens-fragile-peace-in-french-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
